🇵🇹🇵🇹🇵🇹My PORTUGAL diaries continued:
******************************************************
Selfie time with a local florist in beautiful Lisbon at the heart of Rossio Square, the main square in colorful Lisbon. Rossio has been one of the main squares since the Middle Ages and has been a famous setting for celebrations, revolts and even executions. The most striking feature of this square is the patterned tiles mosaic floor which can also be seen on the Copacabana beach in Rio de Janeiro, Brazil 🇧🇷 You can see the patterned mosaic reflecting in my sunglasses :) Beautiful day in Lisbon, PORTUGAL 🇵🇹 #instapassport #instadaily #vscocam #instafollow #portugal #lisbon #instatravel #horizon #florist #indian #flowers #ig_shotz #travelporn #igersportugal #instaselfie #sunglasses #travelpics #justgoshoot  #brasil #portugalalive #travelstoke #lisboa #landscapelovers #colorful #travelblogger #p3top #moodygrams #visualsoflife #livelife #portuguese
